nodes.text: Dawn of the Jedi: Force War 5

Dawn of the Jedi: Force War 5 is the fifth issue in Star Wars: Dawn of the Jedi: Force War, the third story arc miniseries of the Star Wars: Dawn of the Jedi comic book series by John Ostrander and Jan Duursema. Force War 5 was published by Dark Horse Comics on March 19, 2014. It is the final issue not only in the Force War arc, but also for the Dawn of the Jedi storyline as a whole.

The alien Rakata are on the brink of opening the Infinity Gate, ready to unleash their Empire on an unsuspecting galaxy! The Je'daii must win this battle—even if it means the end of their order. But how can they attain victory when their greatest hero has joined the enemy?
